* {{ill|lt=Jogan (Japan)|Q1075635|WD=Q1075635|lt=Jogan|1=Jōgan}} 9 ({{ill|lt=867|Q30347|WD=Q30347|1=867}}), March 10: from Junior Fifth Rank Lower to Junior Fourth Rank Lower (''{{ill|lt=Nihon Sandai Jitsuroku|Q1052981|WD=Q1052981|1=Nihon Sandai Jitsuroku}}'') - written as "Nika no Kami".

