=== Cultural properties ===
=== Yamaguchi City designated cultural properties ===
* Tangible cultural property
** Wooden lion head (sculpture) - early Edo period, made in 1608 (Keicho 13), total length 55.7 cm. Designated March 2, 1982 (Showa 57)<ref name="説明板"/>.

The honden had also been designated a Yamaguchi Prefecture tangible cultural property on November 11, 1977 (Showa 52), but was lost in the 1997 fire.

